{
  "stem": "1132.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was a very religious woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We always celebrated Rosh Hashana, Yom Kippur, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all of the High Holy Days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also always celebrated Pesach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We always observed-- we always had Seders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that is something that is very strong in my memory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were a very small family, so the recollection says to me that it was the immediate family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This one-- I only had this one aunt and uncle that I spoke about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had two daughters, who were substantially older than I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother had some aunts and uncles, so I remember celebrating with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was prior to '44, so that I remember a series of holiday observations.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Although as I said earlier, my mother never kept kosher, but there was always observation of all of the holidays.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was never any question about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As I mentioned, the Germans came in March 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Very little observation of anything was possible after that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have no recollections of observing the High Holy Days in '44.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There could have been some very minimal, but times were really very tough at that point.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And already there was rationing, and there was already the curfew, so things were really not going very well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Obviously, we were-- once we went into hiding, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was very little observation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What I do remember, my mother lit the Shabbat candle for as long as she could while we were in our own apartment with the other two families.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As long as she could do that, she did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But of course, you couldn't buy Shabbat candles.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
